            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has browned, add your <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> and<strong> chipotle paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
